1
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:09,640
General Li

2
00:00:09,640 --> 00:00:11,320
Are those our reinforcements?

3
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:16,040
No...

4
00:00:16,040 --> 00:00:17,520
Run! Run!

5
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:50,680
The Seven Swords of Kunlun

6
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:51,760
have come to aid Chentang!

7
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:55,120
Senior brothers and sisters...

8
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:56,520
Li Jing is here.

9
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,400
Thank you for your assistance.

10
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,360
Saving the common people

11
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:01,640
is the duty of a Cultivator.

12
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,360
Didn't they say Chentang Pass

13
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,000
had no reinforcements left?

14
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:08,160
Chain of Seven Swords!

15
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,800
Shrimp soldiers and crab generals...

16
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,120
however many come,

17
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,120
we'll kill them all!

18
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:36,120
Good!

19
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,040
Li Jing, you knave!

20
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:47,280
You stole the Dragon Clan's ancestral treasure,

21
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,320
the Dragon Pivot of the Nine Rivers.

22
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,960
If you slit your throat in apology,

23
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,600
I will show great mercy

24
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:58,360
and spare the men, women, and children of Chentang Pass.

25
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,480
Otherwise,

26
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,640
when the city falls,

27
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,520
none shall be left alive.

28
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,360
By sunrise tomorrow,

29
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:11,320
I expect your answer.

30
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,200
All right.

31
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,280
That was the last one.

32
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:34,840
Father...

33
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:51,160
I fear that tomorrow's battle

34
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,360
will be even more dangerous.

35
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,080
Is this really worth it?

36
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,120
Don't be foolish.

37
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,800
It's a ploy to break our spirit.

38
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,280
Even without you,

39
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,840
would they really spare Chentang Pass?

40
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:03,840
Exactly.

41
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,200
What that Ninth Prince seeks

42
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,160
is the entire Nine Provinces.

43
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,520
General Li.

44
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:14,040
My Kang'er is only sixteen.

45
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,280
The two of us old folks...

46
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:18,960
our hearts are breaking.

47
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:31,520
A soldier not coming back...

48
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,640
that is his fate.

49
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,080
I still have an eldest son

50
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,720
in the army too.

51
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,800
If he dies in battle,

52
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,800
my old partner and I,

53
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:51,040
risking these old bones,

54
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:55,200
will fight the Sea Clan monsters to the end!

55
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,440
Exterminate the Sea demons!

56
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,680
We will never rest!

57
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,000
Exterminate the Sea demons!

58
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,800
We will never rest!

59
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,840
Sea Clan monsters!

60
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,640
Blood for blood!

61
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,240
General Li!

62
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,720
We are not afraid of sacrifice!

63
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,160
Lead us to keep fighting!

64
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,120
Soldiers!

65
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,520
Fight to the death, never retreat!

66
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,640
Fight to the death, never retreat!

67
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,320
Fight to the death, never retreat!

68
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:16,720
Fight to the death, never retreat!

69
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,720
Fight to the death, never retreat!
